      "planinhalt": "<p>Praktische Versuche zu Themen wie:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ethernet Medium Access Control Layer (Frames)</li>\n<li>Switching (VLAN, Trunking, STP)</li>\n<li>Routing (InterVLAN, statisch, dynamisch, NAT)</li>\n<li>TCP/IP Performance</li>\n<li>IPv6</li>\n<li>DHCP, DNS&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>",
